Package: biLocPol
Type: Package
Title: Bivariate Local Polynomial Estimator
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Max Berger
Maintainer: Max Berger <mberger@mathematik.uni-marburg.de>
Description: Bivariate Local Polynomial estimator for first and 
    second order for bivariate functions and partial derivatives 
    up to order two. Extra case for estimating the covariance 
    kernel for noisy functional data.
